Chen, do you remember?

00:03:57.260 --> 00:03:58.300
This is where we had

00:03:58.430 --> 00:03:59.700
our very first date.

00:04:03.070 --> 00:04:04.440
Ever since that day,

00:04:05.580 --> 00:04:07.140
I've imagined it over and over,

00:04:08.340 --> 00:04:09.860
the two of us getting
married someday,

00:04:10.740 --> 00:04:11.900
having a kid,

00:04:13.340 --> 00:04:14.420
