00:05:29.660 --> 00:05:32.580
I never once hesitated about this.

00:05:36.740 --> 00:05:38.020
Do you know why?

00:05:40.900 --> 00:05:43.140
Because I never imagined
my life without you.

00:05:47.060 --> 00:05:48.820
I know my mom is right.

00:05:51.100 --> 00:05:52.340
We're not married yet,

00:05:54.020 --> 00:05:55.620
and we're still kids ourselves.

00:05:56.700 --> 00:05:57.980
We're not fully mature.

00:06:01.620 --> 00:06:04.660
But who doesn't grow up
through exactly this stage?

00:06:13.820 --> 00:06:14.580
Xu Zhidong.

00:06:15.260 --> 00:06:15.900
I'm here.

00:06:18.100 --> 00:06:20.060
I never planned out what our future

00:06:20.060 --> 00:06:21.220
had to look like.

00:06:25.340 --> 00:06:27.140
Because as long as you're in it,

00:06:29.060 --> 00:06:29.950
that's enough for me.

00:06:44.820 --> 00:06:45.460
Chen,

00:06:47.140 --> 00:06:48.300
will you marry me?

00:06:58.020 --> 00:06:58.900
Of course.

00:07:07.520 --> 00:07:09.900
- This thing is impossible to slip on.
- What are you doing?

