00:07:56.510 --> 00:07:58.700
This belongs to my daughter's
mother-in-law's family.

00:07:58.700 --> 00:07:59.940
It's their heirloom.

00:08:00.260 --> 00:08:02.660
Supposedly passed down for generations.

00:08:02.660 --> 00:08:04.340
I've been appraising jade my whole life.

00:08:04.340 --> 00:08:05.540
You think I'd get it wrong?

00:08:06.140 --> 00:08:07.820
The craftsmanship is decent, though.

00:08:08.380 --> 00:08:09.340
The person who faked it

00:08:09.620 --> 00:08:11.060
must have been a real pro.

