I didn't want them make things
difficult for Mingzhu.

00:08:43.540 --> 00:08:45.420
Why didn't you tell me?

00:08:49.020 --> 00:08:50.700
What's the point?

00:08:53.220 --> 00:08:55.340
It would just make
one more person worry.

00:08:57.300 --> 00:08:58.860
Oh, Xiang,

00:09:01.660 --> 00:09:03.420
I'm your husband.

00:09:04.220 --> 00:09:05.780
Everything that happens in this family

00:09:07.940 --> 00:09:11.460
is something we
should shoulder together,

00:09:12.180 --> 00:09:14.100
