We'll use your pension

00:10:06.620 --> 00:10:08.380
and pay it back month by month.

00:10:08.660 --> 00:10:09.980
No matter how long it takes,

00:10:09.980 --> 00:10:11.340
we'll pay it off.

00:10:11.340 --> 00:10:13.220
Yes, we will.

00:10:13.900 --> 00:10:15.140
As parents,

00:10:16.500 --> 00:10:18.580
we can't keep adding
to the kids' burdens,

00:10:18.980 --> 00:10:20.300
especially Zhixia.

00:10:20.300 --> 00:10:21.580
Yes, I know.

00:10:22.700 --> 00:10:24.020
We can move back to your hometown

00:10:24.900 --> 00:10:26.740
and stay in the old house for now.

00:10:27.140 --> 00:10:28.140
We'll make do.

00:10:30.420 --> 00:10:31.500
Back to the old house.

00:10:36.180 --> 00:10:37.940
That could actually work.

00:10:39.220 --> 00:10:42.900
It's nice and quiet out there.

00:10:43.780 --> 00:10:45.020
It's a good place.

00:10:46.260 --> 00:10:47.740
I grew up in that old house.

00:10:47.740 --> 00:10:49.820
I haven't been back in so long.

00:10:50.340 --> 00:10:50.900
I...

00:10:51.860 --> 00:10:53.780
I'd actually really like to go back.

00:10:56.780 --> 00:10:57.660
Xu Dacheng,

00:11:03.620 --> 00:11:05.140
I'm sorry for putting you through this.

00:11:08.980 --> 00:11:09.780
So basically,

00:11:09.780 --> 00:11:12.020
you asked your boss for two hours off,

00:11:12.020 --> 00:11:13.340
and he approved two days?

00:11:14.460 --> 00:11:15.940
See? My boss is solid.

00:11:17.620 --> 00:11:18.940
Your hotel is probably two steps

00:11:19.460 --> 00:11:20.460
from shutting down.

00:11:20.470 --> 00:11:22.610
I'm thinking twice before
working with you guys again.

00:11:23.620 --> 00:11:24.820
Don't jinx it!

00:11:25.060 --> 00:11:25.700
I'm telling you,

00:11:25.700 --> 00:11:27.980
Nanxi Hotel will stand forever.

00:11:29.540 --> 00:11:30.460
But Mingzhu,

00:11:30.820 --> 00:11:32.420
I don't know if I should say this.

00:11:32.420 --> 00:11:33.820
I know what you're going to say.

00:11:34.700 --> 00:11:36.260
You can't expect every woman

00:11:36.260 --> 00:11:38.340
to want to be a mother
just because I'm pregnant.

00:11:39.980 --> 00:11:41.660
No, you don't understand the situation.

00:11:42.340 --> 00:11:43.260
Bichen wants

00:11:43.420 --> 00:11:45.020
to keep the baby herself.

00:11:45.300 --> 00:11:48.140
Her mom was just furious
and was forcing her to get an abortion.

00:11:48.360 --> 00:11:50.100
Even so, that's not
your place to interfere.

00:11:50.440 --> 00:11:51.900
I didn't want to get involved either.

00:11:52.460 --> 00:11:53.500
But what could I do?

00:11:53.500 --> 00:11:54.700
I was just pulled into it.

00:11:56.780 --> 00:11:58.660
Blood ties are strange,

00:11:59.580 --> 00:12:00.860
like something you can't outrun.

00:12:01.740 --> 00:12:02.420
I'm pretty.

00:12:03.060 --> 00:12:05.660
I don't have time to debate the origin
of life with you today.

00:12:05.820 --> 00:12:07.380
I have to bring lunch to Mr. Hu.

00:12:07.380 --> 00:12:08.820
Again?

00:12:09.520 --> 00:12:11.760
Who do you think I'm trying
to win over Mr Hu for, huh?

00:12:11.900 --> 00:12:13.620
It's for our future kid.

00:12:13.940 --> 00:12:15.860
So we won't have to worry
about tutoring later.

00:12:16.500 --> 00:12:18.100
Love hides in unexpected places.

00:12:18.860 --> 00:12:19.260
Bye.

00:12:19.540 --> 00:12:21.500
