- Easy.
- Careful.

00:41:38.300 --> 00:41:39.060
Let's go home.

00:41:39.500 --> 00:41:41.060
- We're home.
- Be careful.

00:41:41.980 --> 00:41:43.140
We're home!

00:41:43.500 --> 00:41:44.180
Yes!

